summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 18751, entitled, "An Ordinance providing for the installation of a rock quarry near Deception Pass, Skagit County, Washington, and the purchase of equipment therefor, and appropriating the sum of Thirty-thousand ($30,000) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary for such purpose, and authorizing the leasing of said plant to the State of Washington," approved on the Thirtieth day of June, 1908.
